{"tid":1272698,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[香港自強]服務業篇，香港的客人","createTime":"2019-07-01T12:29:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-01T15:25:31.000Z","uid":59565,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c9c338bdb363349abed8ec4818ca8abc3cad130e","tid":1272698,"uid":59565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T12:29:28.000Z","msg":"由於之前有巴打表示為咗令更多人接受到文章，title會改為香港自強<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n繼講完水資源同食物之後，就講下香港服務貿易，啲人成日話香港無咗中國就唔掂，香港作為服務業為主嘅大城市，究竟各個服務業賺緊中國幾多錢？<br />\n以下係2017年香港嘅服務貿易輸出資料，唔講咁多！睇資料！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">保養及維修服務</span></strong><br />\n貿易輸出總額：2,557百萬 <br />\n中國 425百萬 16.6%<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">美國 1,077百萬 42.1%</span><br />\n新加玻 174百萬 6.8%<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">運輸(香港四大支柱)</span></strong><br />\n貿易輸出總額 237,426百萬<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">中國 63,517百萬 26.8%</span><br />\n美國 39,585百萬 16.7%<br />\n日本 18,146百萬 7.6%<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">旅遊(香港四大支柱)</span></strong><br />\n貿易輸出總額 259,817百萬<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">中國 201,611百萬 77.6%</span><br />\n美國 5,931百萬 2.3%<br />\n日本 3,667百萬 1.4%<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">保險及退休金服務</span></strong><br />\n貿易輸出總額 11,050百萬<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">中國 4,704百萬 43.6%</span><br />\n日本 1,343百萬 12.2%<br />\n美國 394百萬 8.4%<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">金融服務(香港四大支柱)</span></strong><br />\n貿易輸出總額 158,714百萬<br />\n中國 11,849百萬 7.5%<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">英國 32,624百萬 20.6%</span><br />\n美國 26,382百萬 16.6%<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">知識產權使用費</span></strong><br />\n貿易輸出總額 5,605百萬<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">中國 2,037百萬 36.3%</span><br />\n新加坡 619百萬 11%<br />\n美國 584百萬 10.4%<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">電子通訊、電腦及資訊服務</span></strong><br />\n貿易輸出總額 22,076百萬<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">中國 5,794百萬 26.2%</span><br />\n英國 2,771百萬 12.6%<br />\n美國 2,140百萬 9.7%<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">其他商業服務</span></strong><br />\n貿易輸出總額 111,474百萬<br />\n中國 18,764百萬 16.8%<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">美國 34,303百萬 30.8%</span>"},{"pid":"10ea97602587a2b2798205dfc64b0acb1578e8a9","tid":1272698,"uid":59565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T12:30:59.000Z","msg":"屌 未撚打完唔小心早洩"},{"pid":"f4ba362049728fbdddeb70d5e99cab5f0b1d5937","tid":1272698,"uid":52230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T12:33:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a83adb5e61f5eabc2df8e037331208a6d0bf99c","tid":1272698,"uid":9521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T12:36:33.000Z","msg":"使撚講咩,香港本身就係一個美國既橋樑<br />\n因為稅制同匯款問題,就算強國人要出口貨都會開間香港公司<br />\n10間香港貿易公司有9間都係食美國水,一係就相反外國入貨到中國用香港呢個名<br />\n所以經濟上香港唔依賴強國,反而係佢地依賴返香港轉頭<br />\n香港靠大陸人既行業只有過多既藥房,金舖<br />\n就算旅遊業,而家班狗都自由行再即日來回根本唔關佢地事<br />\n香港TOP酒店都係外國人訂多過班低消費垃圾人種"},{"pid":"cf6f99bcdecf2367ecaa462327b4b51a2409a83d","tid":1272698,"uid":260988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T13:43:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"da8d5de6a2dc7f3c9e0a0bf312676929adc296b9","tid":1272698,"uid":260988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T13:43:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fe9009fd3f536fe4ddbb99a98a648e42355e2cdd","tid":1272698,"uid":28307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T15:25:31.000Z","msg":"push"}]}